{
  "stem": "3804.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a lot of talking and-- and only-- only very later-- how do you say?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They accepted each other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The relationship started again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- we used him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used this airplane to bring over-- over Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, what want to say is when I disguised him-- I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I disguised him at the time I knew about the airplane.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know-- how do you say?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the beginning, we didn't know how we're going to bring him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I disguised him, put the hat on him, all this, he said-- he looked in the mirror and said, oh, I like this uniform.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't put the Star of David because I wanted beginning to see-- he liked-- suddenly he felt himself at home with the uniform and everything and all this.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I gave him-- how do you say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I put the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, well, what is this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, now, OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't tell him there's going to be a steward, you know, Israeli steward and all this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after they put a picture and everything and we make him a steward-- and that was the problem that, I don't know, somehow the head of the Secret Service brought a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's written there, [INAUDIBLE] and all this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't-- it didn't succeed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not so important, the whole thing-- I didn't understand what's so important that he will sign on the paper, I'm ready to go to Jerusalem, willingly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if he wouldn't sign, what now do it?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
